# Orphan badges branch — only the two JSON files in .github/badges/ are tracked.
# This branch shares no history with main; the working tree on disk may carry
# files left over from the main branch's checkout. Ignore them all so neither
# the CLI nor GitHub Desktop offers them up as accidental staged changes.

*
!.gitignore
!.github/
.github/*
!.github/badges/
!.github/badges/*.json
